c: 2
v: 221
t: "Wata on resu …ďen rew…ďe shirkay…ďe haa …ďe gom…óina: Mi Woondii ko kor…óo gom…óin…óo …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude debbo shirkoowo hay si o haawnii on. Wata on resin …ďen wor…ďe shirkoo…ďe haa …ďe gom…óina: Mi Woondii ko maccu…óo gom…óin…óo …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude dimo shirkoowo hay si o haawnii on.∆Āen …óon hi…ďe nodda faade e yiite, Alla No Noddude e Aljanna e haforanal, e duŇčyee Makko. Himo ∆ĀaŇčngina Aayeeje Makko …óen wonannde yim…ďe …ďen, belajo'o …ďe wa'ajitoto"